{
  "stem": "18654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they smashed up the synagogues on Kristallnacht, and all the-- and a lot of houses were attacked.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our place wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I've been told the reason for it was because they wanted the Philanthropin kept whole.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was guarded on Kristallnacht because they used it later as a Sammelplatz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They collected the Jews and put them there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was after I left, though.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it still stands today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I believe it's now an old-age home, a Jewish old-age home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can remember-- I can remember the tinkling of glass, the breaking of glass.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't-- we didn't leave the flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father must have-- we must have known a bit what was going to happen because he disappeared, he hid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my uncle, who was ill, was in bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[COUGHING] And why I had remembered it, I suppose, was because I had my little case packed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my mother said to me, will you give your little case to your uncle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're going to take him away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was, I didn't really want to give it to him, but I did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I gave him my little case, which was packed with little bits of food and so on, ready for my own journey.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't remember ever seeing him again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took him out, they dragged him out of his bed and took him away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father, luckily, as I said, had hidden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he appeared the next day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I-- he still was with us until, certainly until I left, my sister and I left, which was in January 1939.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Apart from that, I really can't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and my sister and this uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my father appeared, I think, the next day or the day after.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
